Chat Application:
Client/Server scripting, Even without Server side we can do chat applicaiton using chat engine

1. Chat Services
2. npm install react-chat-engine
3. useState Hook method to handle Messaging (Direct/Personal Chat)

chatengine.io (Create Account and generate API key)

Secret Key, Handle Account Information.

.env file:
CHAT_APP_PROJECT_ID = "project key"
CHAT_APP_USER_SECRET = "secret key"


const App = () =>{
return(

    <ChatEngine username='', projectID='', userKey= ''/>
)

}

export default App